Subject: [PATCH] perf ui browser: Avoid SEGV on title
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.9.4
Git-commit: 90f01afb0dfafbc9b094bb61e61a4ac297d9d0d2

[ Upstream commit 90f01afb0dfafbc9b094bb61e61a4ac297d9d0d2 ]

If the title is NULL then it can lead to a SEGV.

